     <div id="esim1" class="content-section">
        <p>As Helmet libraries' customer you have access to two e-book services and three e-audiobook services.</p>
        <ul class="list-bullets">
          <li>Finnish e-books and e-audiobooks – <a href="https://www.ellibslibrary.com/en/helmet" target="_blank" aria-label="Ellibs. The link opens in a new window.">Ellibs</a></li>
          <li>Foreign e-books and e-audiobooks – <a href="https://helmet.overdrive.com/" target="_blank" aria-label="Overdrive. The link opens in a new window.">OverDrive</a></li>
          <li>English e-audiobooks – <a href="https://helsinkilib.naxosspokenwordlibrary.com/" target="_blank" aria-label="Naxos Spoken Word Library. The link opens in a new window.">
            Naxos Spoken Word Library</a></li>
        </ul>
        <p>To borrow e-books, you will need a Helmet library card and a PIN code, a device suitable for reading, and internet access. If you want to download e-books onto your own device, you 
        will also need an app or a reader application. Below you will find device specific instructions.</p>
